SACRED CHAPEL FOR REAL.

51
00:06:13,916 --> 00:06:15,791
- Hecate: THE SACRED CHAPEL.

52
00:06:15,875 --> 00:06:17,375
- Sydonay:
YOU'RE GOING TO BE BUSY.

53
