IN GREAT DEMAND.

64
00:06:46,541 --> 00:06:47,833
- THAT'S FINE WITH ME.

65
00:06:47,916 --> 00:06:50,583
BUT YOU'RE CERTAIN HECATE
WON'T BE HARMED BY THIS?

66
00:06:50,666 --> 00:06:54,500
- RELAX, THOUSAND CHANGES.
HECATE WILL BECOME ETERNAL,

67
00:06:54,583 --> 00:06:57,208
AND POWER OF EXISTENCE
WILL FLOW FOREVER.

68
