- HMM, WELL, I'LL DO MY PART
TO ENSURE IT HAPPENS.

69
00:07:01,291 --> 00:07:03,416
I JUST WANT TO PROTECT HECATE.

70
00:07:03,500 --> 00:07:06,250
- REMEMBER, I DO NOT
BELONG TO YOU.

71
